Hi <%= @main_signup.name %>,

Here's your volunteering confirmation for <%= @event.title %> on <%= @event.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
from <%= @event.start_time.strftime("%l:%M %p") %> to <%= @event.end_time.strftime("%l:%M %p") %>.
<%= @domain == 'localhost' ? "http://#{@domain}:3001/events/#{@event.id}/signup-confirmation" : "https://#{@domain}/events/#{@event.id}/signup-confirmation" %>

<%= @event.description %>

Here's the info you signed up with:

Name: <%= @main_signup.name %>
Email: <%= @main_signup.email %>
